          "type": "text",
          "text": "Each variant runs all 7 Jira test steps end-to-end. Each variant is isolated in its own test VRF so Step 5 (enable allow-default on one AFI) does not collide with other uRPF interfaces in the same VRF. For every step, "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "show interfaces <IF>",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " and "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "show interfaces detail <IF>",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " produced identical uRPF lines (Pass Criterion #2)."
